Python

Pandas, NumPy

Seaborn, Matplotlib

Collaborative Filtering

Correlation Analysis

ğŸ¯ Key Takeaways

Demonstrates practical recommender system design

Combines statistical reasoning with real-world data

Focuses on scalability and relevance rather than purely academic models
